

<div id="outside">
<form id="survey-form" >
  <h1 id="title">Now, let's find if this item is suitable for you, <%= user.name%>.</h1>
  
  <legend style="text-align: left">Answer the following questions. <br>Please add the prices of the item you're buy according to the prices of Egypt.</legend>

  <p style="text-align: left; font-weight: bold;">1.Rate the quality of this product:</p>
  <div class="rate" style="margin-top: -35px;">
    <input type="radio" id="star5" name="rate" value="5" />
    <label for="star5" title="text">5 stars</label>
    <input type="radio" id="star4" name="rate" value="4" />
    <label for="star4" title="text">4 stars</label>
    <input type="radio" id="star3" name="rate" value="3" />
    <label for="star3" title="text">3 stars</label>
    <input type="radio" id="star2" name="rate" value="2" />
    <label for="star2" title="text">2 stars</label>
    <input type="radio" id="star1" name="rate" value="1" />
    <label for="star1" title="text">1 star</label>
  </div>
  <br>

  <p style="text-align: left; font-weight: bold">2.How many times will you wear this item?</p>

  <div style="text-align: left; margin-top: -46px">
    <label for="TimesPerWeek" style="text-align: left;"></label>
    <p style="padding: 20px">
      <input type="radio" name="timesPerWeek" value="7" checked> Daily<br>
      <input type="radio" name="timesPerWeek" value="1"> 1 time per week<br>
      <input type="radio" name="timesPerWeek" value="2"> 2 times per week<br>
      <input type="radio" name="timesPerWeek" value="3"> 3 times per week<br>
      <input type="radio" name="timesPerWeek" value="4"> 4 times per week<br>
      <input type="radio" name="timesPerWeek" value="5"> 5 times per week<br>
      <input type="radio" name="timesPerWeek" value="6"> 6 times per week

    </p>
  </div>

  
  <p style="text-align: left; font-weight: bold">3.Enter the price of the item? (Only Egypt is handled. So, we accept ج.م.‏ only; other currencies will be added soon.)</p>
  <div class="input-group" style="margin-top: -20px; text-align: left;">
    <label for="price"></label>
    <input id="price"  style="padding: 20px" class="form-control" type="text" required id="" name="price" placeholder="EGP (ج.م.‏)">   </div>


<div>
  <br><br>
</div>


<div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-5">
  <div class="form-group">
    <input   onclick="submitForm('#survey-form', ['input[name=\'rate\']:checked', 'input[name=\'timesPerWeek\']:checked','#price'])" style="margin-top: -49px;" value="Submit your results" class="btn btn-primary">
  </div>

</div>


</form>
  </div>

